# Dreaming Output Templates

## Usage

These templates standardize Dreaming Mode outputs for ACS/OpenClaw agents.

Dreaming reports are structured memory proposals. They are not canonical truth.

Security boundary: do not include secrets, credentials, private keys, wallet seed phrases, auth headers, API tokens, or raw sensitive logs in any template output.

